                    </choice>. le President de la Direction
					<lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>
du Chemin de fer du S<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gotthard
					<lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>
                    <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName> </p>
      </div>
          <div type="opener">
            <p rend="center" xml:id="K_4608_p4">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Mons</abbr>
                        <expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> le President,
		</p>
